<section class="hero" id="inicio">
  <div class="hero-bg"></div>
  <div class="container hero-content">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <p class="hero-label">Estudio Jurídico · Provincia de Buenos Aires</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title">
        Su caso, en manos <em>expertas</em>.
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-desc">
        Soy la Dra. Adriana Ghetti, abogada matriculada.
        Trabajo en dos áreas: <strong>jubilación docente</strong> (con más de 20 años dentro del ámbito educativo)
        y <strong>multas de tránsito</strong>. Lo acompaño en cada paso del trámite, sin vueltas.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a href="https://wa.me/5491169380777?text=Hola%20Dra.%20Ghetti%2C%20quer%C3%ADa%20hacerle%20una%20consulta."
           class="btn btn-primary" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
            <path d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347z"/>
            <path d="M12 0C5.373 0 0 5.373 0 12c0 2.124.554 4.12 1.527 5.855L.057 23.5l5.83-1.527A11.938 11.938 0 0012 24c6.627 0 12-5.373 12-12S18.627 0 12 0zm0 21.818a9.818 9.818 0 01-5.003-1.373l-.36-.214-3.724.977.994-3.63-.235-.373A9.818 9.818 0 1112 21.818z"/>
          </svg>
          Consulta gratuita por WhatsApp
        </a>
        <a href="#servicios" class="btn btn-outline">Ver servicios</a>
      </div>
      <div class="hero-trust">
        <div class="trust-item">
          <strong>+20 años</strong>
          <span>en docencia</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-divider"></div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <strong>Especialista</strong>
          <span>en jubilación docente</span>
        </div>
        <div class="trust-divider"></div>
        <div class="trust-item">
          <strong>Consulta</strong>
          <span>sin costo inicial</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hero-visual">
      <a href="#jubilacion" class="hero-card hero-card--jub">
        <div class="card-icon">🎓</div>
        <h3>Jubilación docente</h3>
        <p>¿Cerca de jubilarte? Antes de iniciar el trámite, pedí tu Informe Técnico Preventivo.</p>
        <span class="card-cta">Ver área →</span>
      </a>
      <a href="#multas" class="hero-card hero-card--multas">
        <div class="card-icon">🚦</div>
        <h3>Multas de tránsito</h3>
        <p>¿Te llegaron multas? Antes de pagar, conviene revisar el caso. Consulta sin cargo.</p>
        <span class="card-cta">Ver área →</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    position: relative;
    background: var(--navy);
    color: var(--white);
    overflow: hidden;
    min-height: 88vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .hero-actions .btn {
    flex: 1 1 auto;
  }

  .hero-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(184,152,106,0.12) 0%, transparent 60%),
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 80%, rgba(36,54,96,0.8) 0%, transparent 50%);
  }

  .hero-content {
    position: relative;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 360px;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
    padding-top: 3rem;
    padding-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .hero-label {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 4.5vw, 3.5rem);
    font-family: var(--font-serif);
    color: var(--white);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    line-height: 1.15;
  }

  .hero-title em {
    color: var(--gold);
    font-style: normal;
  }

  .hero-desc {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.80);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .hero-desc strong {
    color: var(--gold-light);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 1rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .hero-trust {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .trust-item {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
  }

  .trust-item strong {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
  }

  .trust-item span {
    font-size: 0.78rem;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
  }

  .trust-divider {
    width: 1px;
    height: 32px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.2);
  }

  .hero-visual {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-card {
    background: var(--white);
    color: var(--text);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 1.5rem 1.5rem 1.4rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    display: block;
    transition: transform 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s;
    border-top: 4px solid var(--gold);
  }

  .hero-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-3px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 48px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
  }

  .hero-card--multas {
    border-top-color: var(--navy);
  }

  .card-icon {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
    line-height: 1;
  }

  .hero-card h3 {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    color: var(--navy);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-card p {
    font-size: 0.88rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.55;
    margin-bottom: 0.85rem;
  }

  .card-cta {
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--gold);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .hero-card--multas .card-cta {
    color: var(--navy);
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .hero-content {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 2.5rem;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      padding-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-visual {
      flex-direction: column;
      max-width: 480px;
    }
    .hero {
      min-height: auto;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .hero-desc {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .hero-actions {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .hero-actions .btn {
      width: 100%;
    }
    .trust-divider {
      display: none;
    }
    .hero-trust {
      gap: 1rem;
    }
  }
</style>
